OL,4,CTesco Bank to close all its current
OL,5,Caccounts
OL,6, Tesco Bank has said it will close all
OL,7, of its current accounts because most
OL,8, customers are no longer using them.
OL,10,FThe bank has estimated only 12% of its
OL,11,Fcurrent accounts are being used by
OL,12,Fcustomers as their primary account.
OL,14,FIt said most had "limited activity" and
OL,15,Fothers were being used for "other
OL,16,Fpurposes, such as a savings pot".
OL,18,FThe decision comes after the bank
OL,19,Freported a #175m loss in April,
OL,20,Fcompared with a #193m profit in the
OL,21,Fprevious 12 months.
